sentences.english: Nitrate nitrogen removal from ground water by autotrophic denitrification in a packed bed reactor.

sentences.english: Autotrophic oxidation of elemental sulfur is relative weak.

sentences.english: The nitrifying bacteria are chemosynthetic autotrophs.
sentences.chinese: 硝化细菌是化能合成的自养生物。
